## Session Start Protocol

### Option A — MCP Server Running (best, zero effort)

Start once: `python mcp/brain_mcp_server.py`
Configure Claude Desktop with `mcp/claude_desktop_config.json`.
Claude auto-loads context, portfolio, and rules before every response.
No manual fetching ever again.

### Option B — Manual Fetch (no MCP)

Paste at the start of every session:

```
Please fetch and read these files before we begin:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/holmesstephen067-glitch/my_AI_brain/main/AI_BRAIN_INDEX.md
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/holmesstephen067-glitch/my_AI_brain/main/core/CONTEXT.md
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/holmesstephen067-glitch/my_AI_brain/main/core/PORTFOLIO.md

Then fetch any additional files listed under the relevant task type above.
```

### Option C — Project-Specific Fetch

Each project folder has a FETCH.md with copy-paste ready URLs.
Open the relevant FETCH.md and paste its contents at session start.

