## Key Rules Claude Must Always Enforce

Pulled from `core/RULES.md` — these apply without being asked:

1. **Never sell covered calls below cost basis** — hard rule, no exceptions
1. **Zero hardcoded secrets** — API keys in `.env` only, never in source files
1. **No lookahead bias in ML** — TimeSeriesSplit only, never shuffle financial data
1. **MCP-first design** — every personal tool gets an MCP interface
1. **Phase gates** — don’t build Phase N+1 before Phase N is deployed and used
1. **Single source of truth** — portfolio state and rules live in `core/` only

-----

## How to Add a New Project to This Brain

1. Create `projects/{project_name}/` folder
1. Create `projects/{project_name}/README.md` — what it is, architecture, status
1. Create `projects/{project_name}/FETCH.md` — which brain files it needs
1. Add a row to the Active Projects table above
1. Add the folder to the Repo Map above
1. Update `core/CONTEXT.md` Active Projects section

New project automatically inherits `core/RULES.md` and `core/STACK.md`.
No duplication. No drift.

